  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      It is the purpose of this study to attempt to determine if there is an immediate, measurable
      change in visual function as a direct result following a session of cranial osteopathic
      manipulation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
